<subSubSection id="6CA294F37BA1A3EAC394A28C4E8FA0F8" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="54D2B862FDD35682B5A8651575898B53" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="09428B54D151DFEBC3431EB5635364BF" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">
This variety is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="01B6184116881A2380AE6A5AD60EF5DD" authority="var. sohayakiense" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ericaceae" genus="Rhododendron" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="var." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rhododendron sohayakiense var. sohayakiense" order="Ericales" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sohayakiense" variety="sohayakiense">Rhododendron sohayakiense var. sohayakiense</taxonomicName>
Y. Watan. &amp; T. Yukawa and 
<taxonomicName id="8B810E990FA90996BCCBBCB69E3454A4" genus="R." infraspecific-rank="var." lsidName="R. sohayakiense var. kiusianum" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="variety" species="sohayakiense" variety="kiusianum">R. sohayakiense var. kiusianum</taxonomicName>
Y. Watan., T. Yukawa &amp; T. Minamitani, but is distinguished by its large leaf size. Further, it differs from the former through its raised lateral nerves on the abaxial leaf surface and from the latter through its shorter corolla tube and by its longer style exserted from the corolla.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
